Class itml.simulator.StateAgent

java.lang.Object
  itml.simulator.StateAgent

public class itml.simulator.StateAgent
extends java.lang.Object

This class implements the type itml.simulator.StateAgent, which keeps track of the state of an agent (i.e., location, stamina, and health).
